snippet.title: Ascending Inferno | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
**FLASHING LIGHTS WARNING** This video may potentially trigger seizures for people with photosensitive epilepsy. Viewer discretion is advised

Play the Demo for Ascending Inferno on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2442820/Ascending_Inferno/

Experience rage-inducing precision platforming as a recently deceased soccer player damned to Inferno! Kick your sibling's soul out of Hell for your chance at redemption!
